com.github.bogieclj.molecule.system

Class URIFn

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.bogieclj.molecule.system.URIFn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Fn, Function<Param,Param>

    public class URIFn
extends Object
implements Fn
    The URIFn is a wrapper Fn implementation which provides the ability to wrap a Function to provide the ability to specify URI for the Fn as well as support in and out param declarations. This is a convenience class which reduces the need to create multiple Fn classes and provides an easy way to wrap java.util.function.Function classes.
